profile_positions.description:
Edibles focuses on replacing single use tableware (cutlery, crockery) with a sustainable and tasty alternative; Edible Tableware!

Instead of throwing away your paper cup or wooden spoon, why not have a little snack after your food or beverage? And even if you are not hungry you can throw it away with a clean conscious as the items are biodegradable.

Their goal is to reduce the massive amounts of waste generated daily by single use cups, straws, cutlery and others making the world a cleaner place one bite at a time.
